descriptionNullable:
This repo contains the news data in tabular format. Please read about how the data was prepared from different sources:
* [Nepali News (Gorkhapatra) Scrapping Using BeautifulSoup and Python](https://iamdurga.github.io/2021/03/28/nepali-news-scrapping-gorkhapatra/)
* [Nepali News (ekantipur) Scrapping Using BeautifulSoup and Python](https://iamdurga.github.io/2021/03/23/nepali-news-scrapping-ekantipur/)
* [Nepali News (Onlinekhabar Post) Scrapping Using BeautifulSoup and Python](https://iamdurga.github.io/2021/03/19/nepali-news-scrapping-onlinekhabar/)

I have also done some work on this dataset which can be found below blogs:
* [EDA on Nepali News](https://iamdurga.github.io/2022/04/23/nepali-news-analysis-eda/)
* [Nepali News Classification with Naive Bayes](https://iamdurga.github.io/2022/05/07/nepali-news-classification-with-naive-bayes/)
* [Nepali News Classification with Logistic Regression](https://iamdurga.github.io/2022/04/30/nepali-news-classification-with-logistic-regression/)
title: Nepali News Data
subtitle: For EDA and Simple Classification
